gw.api.tree

Class AbstractLazyLoadingTreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.tree.AbstractLazyLoadingTreeNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BeanArrayTreeNode, BeanFieldsTreeNode, BeanTreeNode, CCTeamTreeViewModel, GroupPickerTreeNode, GroupTreeNode, OrganizationTreeNode, TeamTreeNode, UnassignedUsersGroupNode

    public abstract class AbstractLazyLoadingTreeNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements TreeNode
    The abstract base class for TreeNode implementations that only load child data when expand a non-leaf node.

    You can use the concrete Gosu subclass LazyLoadingTreeNode to construct a tree to be used in PCF files.
